Install dependencies:

    $ sudo apt install gcc g++ python3-venv python3-dev libapt-pkg-dev

Create a new virtual environment:

    $ mkdir ~/venv
    $ python3 -m venv ~/venv
    $ source ~/venv/bin/activate

Update pip in the venv:

    $ pip install -U pip

Install the utility:

    $ pip install -r requirements.txt .

Run it:

    $ apt-key-example
